if (!isAddressAllowed(connectedAddr)) {
    dnsRebindingAttempts.increment();
    throw new SSRFException("DNS rebinding attack detected");
}
```

3. **Comprehensive IP Range Blocking**: Block all RFC 1918 private ranges, cloud metadata IPs, and special-use addresses using both Java's built-in methods and manual CIDR checks:
